name: Hope
description: These artworks are tokenised samples from a web work called 'To The Ghost Nets', hosted on my website www.lewkwilmshurst.co.uk. They also feature in a show commissioned by the Museum of Contemporary Art Busan - May/September 2021. This work was made in collaboration with Tom Johnson and Heinrich Schwarzer. These are some pieces of things. Fragments of the stuff that makes up everything. Maybe they do things together? Maybe they are keys for a lock not yet made?...
